----OBJECTIVE-----

	Vivi has been working on studying and taking care of his antfarm for a while now. Someone in his school doesn't like him and decides to destroy his antfarm. Hearing this news vivi rushes to get his friends AND PROTECT WHAT IS RIGHTFULLY HIS!!. 
- this epic battle takes place in two settings 1. the antfarm - you start in the ant farm and work your way out to grow to normal size. 2. the Lab - you play as a big peron here and the ant farms are located on the tables.

----- why I made the map-----

I made this map for 1.6 and i decided to bring it back with a lil spice. Once i finished this map i realized i want to make a map pack of small to big maps. I have already made De_sony-psp and im going to make another. (hint fish bowl hint) so enjoy my map everyone i spent a good deal working on the textures and the floor tiles are custom. remodled after my schools.
